data.meta_description: Princesse Tam Tam — "Princess Tam Tam is a Pygmalion-like comedy in which Baker stars as a mischievous shepherd girl who rises through society to become the toast of Paris nightlife. In the tradition of 42nd Street, Zou Zou tells the story of a talented Cinderella who saves a show and becomes an overnight sensation"--Container.
